title: The Big Suey: The New York B-Teams
description:
Billy's Marlins helped Stugotz's Mets stay alive to win the NL East, so we take a trip through why Mets fans are so insecure and how it feels to play spoiler when you're helping a team you hate. Then, Stugotz torches Matthew Stafford and vigorously defends Jimmy G which leads us to dueling lists: Mike's Top 5 Worst Super Bowl Winning QBs and Stu's Top 5 Most Overrated Super Bowl Winning QBs. Plus, an interview with CrossFit Games Champion, the fittest on earth, Tia-Clair Toomey.
